{
  "stem": "18626.9",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 337.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My lung busted, and it was rubbing inside in my ribs, and had high fever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they took me to Schwabing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was in Schwabing I think maybe about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all the doctors took me to the x-rays and gave me a big injections.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And some of the, one doctor, professor in the x-ray room called in assistant, young, you know, doctors, to see my lung.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If it would have taken another three or four days more, my lung would have been blood clot, all blood would come out because it was all, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all, you know, sore from the ribs, you know, was torn, the lung and rubbing on the ribs.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember the way he described to the doctors, to the other German doctors, young doctors, you see, that was a bad situation.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As they gave me in the hospital, I remember, big injections.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's called, I think, calcium lacticum, very big needles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I used to get injection, I start to feel heat all over, right to my toes, bottles like that, with injections.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it took two weeks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from when I started to get better, they transferred me to a regular hospital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's called St.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Ottelien.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was actually a choice for missionaries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Catholic missionaries, priests, and monks belong that place, St.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Ottelien.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But in the war times, they made a hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They chased out the monks, you know, and the nuns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they made for the Germans, a hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then when the Americans came, the SS and all the Germans had to leave.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And all the sick liberated prisoners from all the camps were transfer to St.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Ottelien.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when I came to--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then was already Jewish doctors who were liberated and assistant German doctors.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
